latestIgtvVideos.title: P&G Shiksha | Munni
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
“Munni” - a heartwarming story depicting 2 parallel worlds around us. One world where the slightest disturbance in school is a big matter of concern & the other world that struggles to get basic access to education. This story depicts how P&G Shiksha together with your help is enabling education for millions of such children who do not have access to education.
When you choose a P&G Product, you help P&G provide online education to millions of children and build schools for their future.
Since the last 16 years, P&G Shiksha along with your support has helped build 2300 schools which will support 2 million+ children.
During the pandemic, P&G Shiksha helped 50,000 children get online education.
 
To know more about P&G Shiksha's initiatives and impact, visit: https://pgshiksha.com/
#ChooseForShiksha #PadhegaIndiaBadegaIndia #EducationForAll #PGShiksha
